  "body": "A. von Kienlin (MPE) and  V. Connaughton (UAH)\nreport on behalf of the Fermi GBM Team:\n\n\"Since the first 18 triggers from AXP 1E1547.0-5408 detected\nby the Fermi Gamma-ray Burst Monitor on 22 January 2009 \n(GCN 8835, Connaughton & Briggs), there have been 13 additional\ntriggers of Fermi GBM from this source.\nThe GBM on-board locations are all consistent with\nthe AXP 1E1547.0-5408 position. So there are a total of \n31 triggered bursts from this source. Many other bursts\nwere recorded during times where GBM was still in trigger mode.\n\nList of all GBM triggers since the first trigger on 00:53:52.17 UT:\n\n#   Trigcat          Trigger     UTC          \n----------------------------------------------\n 1  GBM 090122.037   254279434   00:53:52.17\n 2  GBM 090122.044   254279035   01:03:53.93\n 3  GBM 090122.052   254279656   01:14:14.88\n 4  GBM 090122.059   254280306   01:25:04.31\n 5  GBM 090122.104   254284211   02:30:09.39\n 6  GBM 090122.113   254284945   02:42:23.17\n 7  GBM 090122.120   254285611   02:53:29.75\n 8  GBM 090122.129   254286352   03:05:50.39\n 9  GBM 090122.173   254290113   04:08:31.65\n10  GBM 090122.180   254290769   04:19:27.62\n11  GBM 090122.187   254291369   04:29:27.73\n12  GBM 090122.194   254291971   04:39:29.95\n13  GBM 090122.218   254294023   05:13:41.02\n14  GBM 090122.243   254296159   05:49:17.55\n15  GBM 090122.252   254297017   06:03:36.00\n16  GBM 090122.283   254299678   06:47:56.78\n17  GBM 090122.291   254300306   06:58:24.25\n18  GBM 090122.310   254301991   07:26:29.66\n19  GBM 090122.317   254302590   07:36:28.75\n20  GBM 090122.352   254305576   08:26:14.53\n21  GBM 090122.359   254306192   08:36:30.55\n22  GBM 090122.380   254308060   09:07:38.67\n23  GBM 090122.390   254308862   09:21:00.39\n24  GBM 090122.419   254311386   10:03:04.66\n25  GBM 090122.428   254312201   10:16:39.36\n26  GBM 090122.451   254314172   10:49:30.19\n27  GBM 090122.491   254317583   11:46:21.33\n28  GBM 090122.498   254318256   11:57:34.06\n29  GBM 090122.551   254322796   13:13:14.53\n30  GBM 090122.584   254325635   14:00:33.44\n31  GBM 090122.624   254329074   14:57:52.72\n\nSpectral analysis results will be reported soon.\""
